N.Y. MaCmillan and Co., 1927. Fine / Very Good. Item #001309A

A fine copy in a very good jacket/brodart covered. Paper labels to spine are in excellent condition. Jacket is clipped to top and bottom of fold, original $2.50 price is intacted. Couple of tiny tears and chips. Soiling to rear panel. A decent copy. Bleiler, The Guide to Supernatural Fiction 342.
